# Howto add mor Security to Debian

This is for small desktop systems 

### Update regular

Add the following line to /etc/apt/sources.list

~~~
deb http://security.debian.org/ jessie/updates main contrib non-free
~~~

Use commands:

~~~
apt-get update
apt-get upgrade
~~~

### Deactivate PRC

~~~
apt-get remove portmap
apt-get autoremove
~~~